snippet.title: GAMBIT! - Gameplay Trailer | Meta Quest 2 | SteamVR (2023)
snippet.description:
Gun up and wreak havoc in Gambit!, a 4-player campaign-driven #vr shooter-adventure set in a world of gangs, guns, and mayhem! 
Coming to Meta Quest 2 and SteamVR with cross-play in 2023.

Wishlist on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1736120/Gambit/
Follow on Twitter: https://twitter.com/GambitTheGame
Join our Discord: https://discord.gg/xrealgames
